title: Neri Kitchen - Pop up
description: Usually twice a month uses the space of Common Cafe at 大阪市北区中崎西1-1-6 to offer a vegan Japanese style lunch, pilaf or curry, plus cake, coffee, and tea. Must call ahead to check.
streetAddress: Osaka-shi, Kita-ku, Nakazaki-nishi 1-1-6, Yoshimura Building B1F
